Hi log gathering task goes as below:

## the top 5 components chosen pls see below: 1. Installer
2. firefox
3. printer
4. network
5. yast2/ zypper

    boot (scenario to cover issue happens during boot up)

## log files for each components

### baseinfo

    gathering (cpuInfo partitionInfo osInfo)

+ cpuInfo: echo `cat /proc/cpuinfo |grep "model name"| uniq -c`
+ partitionInfo: fdisk -l /dev/sda
+ osInfo: echo `cat /etc/YaST2/build`

### installer
- /var/log/pbl.log

### firefox
-

### printer

### network
- ifconfig >ifconfigInfo.txt
- journalctl -u NetworkManager-dispatcher.service -u NetworkManager.service > network.txt

### yast2/ zypper
- /


