options:
\t -h: will print this options manual \n 
\n
components: \n
\t instaler: this will collect logs when you would like to report bugs related with installer \n
\t firefox: this will collect log files related with firefox component \n
\t yast2: this will collect both yast2 and zypper related log files \n
\t printer: this will collect log files for printer issue \n
\t network: this will collect log files for network issue \n
\n
scenaros: \n
\t boot: this wil collect log files for debugging issue happens during boot"`
